[1] Write the full form and one-line use of: HTTP, HTTPS, FTP, SMTP.
    =>HTTP
    HyperText Transfer Protocol
    Used to transfer web pages and data between a web browser and a web server.
    HTTPS
    HyperText Transfer Protocol Secure
    Used to transfer web pages securely by encrypting the data exchanged between the browser and server.
    FTP
    File Transfer Protocol
    Used to upload and download files between computers over a network.
    SMTP
    Simple Mail Transfer Protocol
    Used to send and transfer email messages over the Internet.

[2] What is the difference between IPv4 and IPv6? Answer in 2 lines.
    =>IPv4 uses a 32-bit address and provides about 4.3 billion unique IP addresses.
    IPv6 uses a 128-bit address and provides a much larger number of unique addresses to support the growing Internet. 

